UG Thesis LaTeX Template for Dr. B. C. Roy Engineering College
Version: 3.0
Created: July 2025
Author: Kingsuk Majumdar

This template includes:
- ugthesis.cls: Main LaTeX class file for undergraduate thesis formatting
- Frontmatter templates: Declaration, Certificate, Abstract, Acknowledgment
- Backmatter templates: Author biographies, abbreviations list
- Sample chapter templates and bibliography setup
- Automated formatting for student information, supervisors, and college details

Features:
- Professional A4 formatting optimized for academic thesis
- Support for up to 5 students with automatic conditional rendering
- Integrated photo handling for author biographies
- Customizable headers, footers, and title pages
- Background logo support for certificate pages
- Justified text without hyphenation
- MATLAB code highlighting support via mcode.sty
- Comprehensive error handling and wrapper commands

Usage:
1. Modify main.tex with your thesis details
2. Update student, supervisor, and college information
3. Add your content to chapter files
4. Compile with pdflatex

For support and updates, contact: [Your Email/GitHub]

